There aren't too many venues perfect for a quick happy hour after work AND/OR a complete Friday or Saturday night out from start to finish, but Blue Martini at Town Square really has it down.
Despite that fact that this venue is ALWAYS packed and there's rarely a place to sit (thus the 4-star rating instead of 5) Blue Martini is the perfect setting for someone who doesn't want the club scene, but isn't necessarily looking for a laid back lounge either.
It radiates with energy and style without the obnoxious meat-market factor.
Take a few girlfriends and order the Cherry Bomb martini - "Three Olives" Cherry Vodka, Red Bull Energy Drink and a dash of Grenadine.

