Ladies can get a free VIP card on Wednesday nights which entitles them to a FREE Van Gogh vodka martini or cocktail EVERY TIME THEY COME TO THE BAR.
Just show your VIP card and ID at the door and they will give you a coupon.
They have 8 million martinis to pick from which are all excellent.
The Pomegranate and the Palm Beacher are my favorites.
They recently added quite a few new ones too.
