I will not insult truly top-of-the-kingdom industry people by wagging my tongue over very good fare.
We all, as consumers pay a lot for the opportunity to eat mostly decent food and drink mediocre cocktails, so let's set the bar a little higher, ok?, so that real players can shine and excellence can make it to the forefront.
